    Class Description
    DirectoryIdentifier
    This program enumerates Image File Directory (IFD) types typically found within TIFF image files.

    IFDHandler
    This IFDHandler parses TIFF-based files (such as standard TIFF, EXIF in JPEGs, and DNG) by reading and interpreting Image File Directories (IFDs) within the file's binary structure.
